688
00:35:30,833 --> 00:35:31,833
I'm not Caesar.

689
00:35:32,458 --> 00:35:33,458
No, you're not.

690
00:35:34,875 --> 00:35:36,833
But you're trying to solve this situation.

691
00:35:39,208 --> 00:35:40,208
That's a start.

692
00:35:43,458 --> 00:35:45,458
[sweeping music playing]

693
00:35:49,083 --> 00:35:51,083
[dramatic music playing]

694
00:36:12,041 --> 00:36:13,250
[whines]

695
00:36:18,541 --> 00:36:21,416
- [choral music playing on radio]
- [cart rattling]

696
00:36:26,250 --> 00:36:29,833
If you want to find him,
you need to find him.

697
00:36:30,708 --> 00:36:32,375
Have you found Jesus Christ?

698
00:36:32,458 --> 00:36:34,083
Well, we're a member of the church.

699
00:36:34,166 --> 00:36:36,083
We probably don't go
as often as we should.

700
00:36:37,541 --> 00:36:39,458
- You're selling those?
- Best in the county.

701
00:36:39,958 --> 00:36:41,916
I've got the perfect one for ya.

702
00:36:51,916 --> 00:36:55,041
Saint Anthony
is the patron saint of lost souls.

703
00:36:55,125 --> 00:36:57,291
He'll help bring Gonker's soul
back to you.

704
00:36:58,625 --> 00:36:59,625
Let us pray.

705
00:37:01,000 --> 00:37:05,250
Saint Anthony, guide these men
as they search for their beloved hound.

706
00:37:06,208 --> 00:37:07,208
Amen.

707
00:37:08,250 --> 00:37:09,250
Amen.

708
00:37:09,666 --> 00:37:12,208
Um, well, here's a ten.

709
00:37:12,291 --> 00:37:14,833
Five for the figurine
and five for the prayer.

710
00:37:15,333 --> 00:37:16,500
Appreciate you.

711
00:37:16,583 --> 00:37:17,833
Same to you, brother.

712
00:37:26,333 --> 00:37:28,958
[hopeful music playing]

713
00:37:31,083 --> 00:37:32,083
Can't hurt.

714
00:37:35,708 --> 00:37:38,666
And his collar
is blue and white herringbone.

715
00:37:38,750 --> 00:37:41,750
[woman] <i>I'm real sorry, but none
of our dogs match that description.</i>

716
00:37:42,250 --> 00:37:46,000
Okay. Well, maybe could you just
put up a flyer in the office?

717
00:37:46,083 --> 00:37:46,916
Can do.

718
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:48,375
And I'll make a bunch of copies

719
00:37:48,458 --> 00:37:51,333
and have our shelter volunteers
pass them out around town.

720
00:37:51,416 --> 00:37:53,291
Jerry Malcolm.

721
00:37:54,625 --> 00:37:57,625
Thank you so much.
