1435
01:19:33,333 --> 01:19:35,416
<i>Anything other than water makes me hurt.</i>

1436
01:19:35,916 --> 01:19:38,500
<i>I thought it was just
an upset stomach at first, but</i>

1437
01:19:39,000 --> 01:19:40,750
<i>a few weeks ago, it got really bad.</i>

1438
01:19:42,125 --> 01:19:43,125
Peyton,

1439
01:19:44,125 --> 01:19:45,375
