1440
01:19:45,875 --> 01:19:47,416
Why didn't you tell anyone?

1441
01:19:47,500 --> 01:19:49,083
'Cause I had to keep looking.

1442
01:19:49,166 --> 01:19:50,916
Okay, no, listen to me.

1443
01:19:51,000 --> 01:19:54,750
